#. Description of the plugin
#: msv-magic-link-auth.php
msgid "Passwordless magic-link authentication with rate limiting, an optional protected page, Cloudflare Turnstile support, and a disposable-email blocklist. Works via a shortcode or an Elementor Pro form action."
msgstr ""

